Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.90,Default,,0,0,8,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}影片压制: 九洲客 　字幕调校: 子贺居士　招募Q号: 76846146
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,面试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我和尤尔曼先生有约\N{\rEng}Hi. I've got an appointment with Mr. Ullman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是杰克·特朗斯\N{\rEng}My name is Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他的办公室在一楼的左边\N{\rEng}His office is the first door on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尤尔曼先生?\N{\rEng}Mr. Ullman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是杰克·特朗斯\N{\rEng}I'm Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快进来 杰克\N{\rEng}Come on in, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 非常高兴见到你 - 我也是\N{\rEng}- Very nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的秘书 苏西\N{\rEng}This is my secretary, Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏西 你好 - 我们这儿很难找吧?\N{\rEng}- Susie, how do you do? - Any trouble finding us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不难找 到这儿我才花了三个半小时\N{\rEng}No problem at all. I made the trip in 3 1/2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,算是非常顺利了\N{\rEng}That's very good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍坐一会 杰克\N{\rEng}Sit down a minute, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,随意 不要拘束\N{\rEng}Just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要来点咖啡吗?\N{\rEng}Like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的话 我想尝一尝 谢谢\N{\rEng}If you're having some, I wouldn't mind. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏西 - 好的 先生\N{\rEng}- Susie. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便请比尔·华生过来\N{\rEng}And ask Bill Watson to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rEng}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你真打算 整个冬天都住那个旅馆吗?\N{\rEng}Do you really want to go and live in that hotel for the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当然我愿意\N{\rEng}Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定会很有趣\N{\rEng}It'll be lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我也这么认为\N{\rEng}Yeah. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 那儿恐怕没有人可以陪我玩\N{\rEng}Anyway, there's hardly anybody to play with around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 交新朋友总要花些时间的\N{\rEng}I know. lt always takes a little time to make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 恐怕是\N{\rEng}Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼怎样想呢?\N{\rEng}What about Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他很期待去住那个旅馆 我敢打赌\N{\rEng}He's looking forward to the hotel, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,错 我并不期待 特朗斯太太\N{\rEng}No, I ain't, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 托尼 不要淘气\N{\rEng}Now, come on, Tony. Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想去那个地方\N{\rEng}I don't want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不想去呢?\N{\rEng}How come you don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不想而已\N{\rEng}I just don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们走着瞧\N{\rEng}Let's just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我们会有个愉快的冬天\N{\rEng}We're all going to have a real good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔 这位是杰克·特朗斯\N{\rEng}Bill, I'd like you to meet Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 比尔\N{\rEng}How do you do, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 非常高兴认识你 - 很荣幸\N{\rEng}- Nice to meet you. - Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,找个位子坐 比尔 我们开始吧\N{\rEng}Grab a chair, Bill. Join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克准备为我们 在这个冬天照顾遥望旅馆\N{\rEng}Jack is going to take care of the Overlook for us this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们这边告个段落 你就带他去逛逛\N{\rEng}I'd like you to take him around soon as we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克是位老师\N{\rEng}Jack is a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是位老师\N{\rEng}Formerly a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在干什么?\N{\rEng}What line of work are you in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,写作\N{\rEng}I'm a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠教书 收支还是平衡不了\N{\rEng}Teaching's been more or less a way of making ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对你而言 这是很大的转变吧?\N{\rEng}This ought to be quite a change for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我正是在寻求转变\N{\rEng}I'm looking for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在丹佛的人都强烈推荐杰克 而且我立刻就...\N{\rEng}Our people in Denver recommended Jack very highly, and for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,赞成了他们的意见\N{\rEng}...I agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 我们讲到哪里了?\N{\rEng}Let's see, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我正打算解说...\N{\rEng}I was about to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是在5月15号到10月30号营业\N{\rEng}...that our season here runs from May 15th to October 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们会歇业 直到下个5月来临\N{\rEng}Then we close down completely until the following May.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以问问是为什么吗?\N{\rEng}Do you mind if I ask why you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就我所见 在这边滑雪将是非常美妙的事\N{\rEng}It seems to me that the skiing up here would be fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是肯定的 但是 问题在于庞大的开销...\N{\rEng}It would be. The problem is the enormous cost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为此我们必须保持道路通畅\N{\rEng}...it would be to keep the road to Sidewinder open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而道路绵延25英哩\N{\rEng}It's a 25-mile stretch of road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到了冬天 积雪会厚达20英尺\N{\rEng}It gets 20 feet of snow during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要保持道路通畅的话...\N{\rEng}There's just no way to make it economically feasible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是没有什么经济效益\N{\rEng}...to keep it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,自1907年这个地方被修建以来...\N{\rEng}When the place was built in 1907...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很少有人对这儿的冬季运动感兴趣的\N{\rEng}...there was very little interest in winter sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方是因为它的 与世俗隔绝和风光明媚而闻名\N{\rEng}This site was chosen for its seclusion and scenic beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 不只如此而已\N{\rEng}It's certainly got plenty of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不错\N{\rEng}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,丹佛的人有没有告诉过你...\N{\rEng}Did they give you any idea in Denver...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个工作的负担?\N{\rEng}...about what the job entails?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只说了个大概\N{\rEng}Only in a very general way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,冬季总是难以想像的酷寒\N{\rEng}The winters can be fantastically cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,工作内容是维修工作 防止带来重大损失...\N{\rEng}The basic idea is to cope with the very costly damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和其它一些相关的事\N{\rEng}...and depreciation which can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其实主要就是要照顾锅炉...\N{\rEng}This consists mainly of running the boiler...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都要加热 保持旅馆各个角落的温暖...\N{\rEng}...heating different parts of the hotel on a daily rotating basis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有损坏发生就要修复...\N{\rEng}...repairing damage as it occurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,持续维护使损坏无法产生\N{\rEng}...and doing repairs so the elements can't get a foothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我而言是没有问题的\N{\rEng}That sounds fine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,其实上这工作 真的没有什么太高的要求\N{\rEng}Physically, it's not a very demanding job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 冬季唯一真正要克服的...\N{\rEng}The only thing that can get a bit trying here during the winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是巨大的被隔离感\N{\rEng}...is a tremendous sense of isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那正好是我要寻求的东西\N{\rEng}That just happens to be exactly what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我正构思一部新的作品\N{\rEng}I'm outlining a new writing project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,五个月的安静生活 正符合我所需\N{\rEng}Five months of peace is just what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 杰克\N{\rEng}That's very good, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 对某些人...\N{\rEng}Because, for some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...孤独...\N{\rEng}...solitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...和隔离...\N{\rEng}...and isolation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...会是一个很大的问题\N{\rEng}...can, of itself, become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对我而言不是\N{\rEng}Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的妻子和儿子呢? 你认为他们没问题吧?\N{\rEng}How about your wife and son? Do you think they'll take to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会喜欢的\N{\rEng}They'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在我把你交给比尔以前...\N{\rEng}Before I turn you over to Bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我还有一件事 不得不和你讲\N{\rEng}...there's one other thing I think we should talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吓唬人...\N{\rEng}Not to sound melodramatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这的确会让某些人\N{\rEng}...but it's been known to give a few people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,重新考虑能否接受这个工作\N{\rEng}...second thoughts about the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感兴趣\N{\rEng}I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为 丹佛的人一定没有提到这个...\N{\rEng}I don't suppose they said anything in Denver...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,1970年在这儿发生的悲剧\N{\rEng}...about the tragedy we had up here during the winter of 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的确没有\N{\rEng}I don't believe they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的前任...\N{\rEng}My predecessor in this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雇佣了一个叫查尔斯·格瑞第 担任冬季看管员的工作\N{\rEng}...hired a man named Charles Grady as the winter caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他带着妻子和两个女儿 一个8一个10岁左右\N{\rEng}He came up with his wife and 2 little girls of about 8 and 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他有着良好的工作记录和介绍人\N{\rEng}He had a good employment record, good references.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就我刚才所言 他似乎...\N{\rEng}And from what I've been told, he seemed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一个安全正常的人一样\N{\rEng}...like a completely normal individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是冬季的某天...\N{\rEng}But at some point during the winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定受到了巨大的精神折磨\N{\rEng}...he must have suffered some kind of a complete mental breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然后疯狂地...\N{\rEng}He ran amuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,用斧头 杀了全家人\N{\rEng}...and killed his family with an ax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体全堆到西翼的一个房间里...\N{\rEng}Stacked them neatly in a room in the west wing, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来福枪装了两发子弹 含在嘴里击发\N{\rEng}...he put both barrels of his shotgun in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,警察认为...\N{\rEng}The police thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是以前所谓的幽闭恐慌症\N{\rEng}...that it was what the old-timers used to call cabin fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一种幽闭式的反应 发生在...\N{\rEng}A kind of claustrophobic reaction which can occur...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,人被封闭在一起 经过一段相当长时间后\N{\rEng}...when people are shut in together over long periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个故事...\N{\rEng}That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,实在很刺激\N{\rEng}...quite a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,到现在我还是无法相信 它就发生在这个地方 就是这儿\N{\rEng}It's still hard for me to believe it actually happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 它的确是\N{\rEng}But it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你能理解 我为什么要告诉你这些\N{\rEng}I think you can appreciate why I wanted to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然可以\N{\rEng}I certainly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我还可以理解 为什么丹佛的人...\N{\rEng}I also understand why your people in Denver...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,留着这件事 让你来告诉我\N{\rEng}...left it for you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,显然 一些人会退缩...\N{\rEng}Obviously, some people can be put off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿意待在发生过这种事的地方\N{\rEng}...from staying in a place where something like that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以放心 这不会发生在我身上\N{\rEng}You can rest assured that's not going to happen with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,至于我的妻子...\N{\rEng}And as far as my wife is concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我确定告诉她以后 她一定会很着迷\N{\rEng}...I'm sure she'll be absolutely fascinated when I tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个忠实的鬼故事迷...\N{\rEng}She's a confirmed ghost story...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...和恐怖片迷\N{\rEng}...and horror film addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼 你认为爸爸会得到那份工作吗?\N{\rEng}Tony, do you think Dad'll get the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经得到了\N{\rEng}He already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他马上就会打电话告诉温蒂\N{\rEng}He's going to phone Wendy up in a few minutes to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 宝贝 - 嗨 亲爱的 事情进行得怎样?\N{\rEng}- Hi, babe. - Hi, hon. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我还在旅馆里 而且还有许多地方还没去看过\N{\rEng}Great. I'm at the hotel and I still have a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为9点或10点前 我可能到不了家\N{\rEng}I don't think I can get home before 9 or 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来你得到这份工作了\N{\rEng}Sounds like you got the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这儿真是个漂亮的地方\N{\rEng}Right. It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你和丹尼会喜欢上它的\N{\rEng}You and Danny are going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼 你为什么不想去那个旅馆?\N{\rEng}Tony, why don't you want to go to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 好了 告诉我吧\N{\rEng}You do too know. Now come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我不想告诉你\N{\rEng}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 托尼 告诉我吧\N{\rEng}Now, Tony, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在睁开眼睛 我来检查\N{\rEng}Now, hold your eyes still so I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 另一只眼睛\N{\rEng}That's good. Now the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子\N{\rEng}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 丹尼...\N{\rEng}Now, Danny...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在你刷牙的时候\N{\rEng}...when you were brushing your teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得你闻到一些怪味\N{\rEng}...do you remember if you smelled anything funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,或者看见闪光 和其它一些怪东西吗?\N{\rEng}...or saw any bright, flashing lights or anything at all strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那你记得你在刷牙么?\N{\rEng}Do you remember when you were brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 刷牙之后呢? 你记得发生过什么事情吗?\N{\rEng}What's the next thing you remember after you were brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈对我说 "醒醒 丹尼 醒醒"\N{\rEng}My mom was saying, "Wake up. Wake up, Danny, wake up."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能否记得在刷牙前...\N{\rEng}Can you remember what you were doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做些什么吗?\N{\rEng}...just before you started brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和托尼说话\N{\rEng}Talking to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是你的宠物之一吗?\N{\rEng}Is Tony one of your animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 他是住在我嘴里的小男孩\N{\rEng}No. He's a little boy that lives in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是他想像中的朋友\N{\rEng}Tony's his imaginary friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你现在张开嘴 我能看见托尼吗?\N{\rEng}If you were to open your mouth now, could I see Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不行?\N{\rEng}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他藏起来了\N{\rEng}Because he hides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他藏在什么地方?\N{\rEng}Where does he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我的胃里面\N{\rEng}To my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼有要你去做过什么吗?\N{\rEng}Does Tony ever tell you to do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再谈论托尼了\N{\rEng}I don't want to talk about Tony anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 丹尼\N{\rEng}All right, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我要请你帮我个忙...\N{\rEng}I'm going to ask you to do me a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天都乖乖地待在床上 好吗?\N{\rEng}...and stay quietly in bed for the rest of the day. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要这样吗?\N{\rEng}Do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我希望你这样\N{\rEng}Yes. I'd like you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去另外的房间说几句话\N{\rEng}We're going in the other room for a few minutes and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我会来看你的\N{\rEng}I'll come back and check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们去客厅吗? - 是的\N{\rEng}- Shall we go into the living room? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请坐 - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- Please. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,特朗斯太太 我认为你没有什么好担心的\N{\rEng}Mrs. Torrance, I don't think you have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信丹尼身体健康\N{\rEng}I'm quite sure there's nothing physically wrong with Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在看起来非常好\N{\rEng}He seems absolutely fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你还是应该检查一下\N{\rEng}But you should've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子往往会吓着你\N{\rEng}Kids can scare you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是相信我 那些并不算反常\N{\rEng}But believe me, these episodes are not at all uncommon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们往往比表面看起来要好很多\N{\rEng}And they look much worse than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 他到底是怎么了?\N{\rEng}But what was the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数时候 发生在小孩子身上 某些事情是无法依常理解释的\N{\rEng}Most of the time, these episodes with kids are never explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一些情绪上的原因 而且基本上很少再发生\N{\rEng}They're brought on by emotional factors and rarely occur again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,和自我催眠很相似...\N{\rEng}They're more akin to autohypnosis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一种自我诱导的恍惚状态\N{\rEng}...a kind of self-induced trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 假如再发生的话 我认为...\N{\rEng}If it reoccurs, which I doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以试着做些检查\N{\rEng}...we can always think about having some tests done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信你是对的\N{\rEng}I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你住在博得很久了吗?\N{\rEng}Have you been in Boulder long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只有三个月左右\N{\rEng}Only about three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是佛蒙得州来的 我丈夫以前在那边的学校教书\N{\rEng}We're from Vermont. My husband was teaching school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼想像中的朋友出现在...\N{\rEng}Did the appearance of Danny's imaginary friend....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼\N{\rEng}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 托尼的情况 最早发生在你们到这儿的时候吗?\N{\rEng}Did Tony's first appearance happen to coincide with your arrival here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想...\N{\rEng}Let's see....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼和托尼说话...\N{\rEng}I guess Danny started talking to Tony...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是在我们送他去幼儿园时开始的\N{\rEng}...about the time we put him in nursery school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他适应学校生活吗?\N{\rEng}Did he adjust well to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他最开始并不喜欢学校\N{\rEng}He didn't like it too much at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 之后他受了伤 然后我们就把他留在家里一段时间...\N{\rEng}Then he had an injury, so we kept him out for a while and....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我最早 注意到他和托尼交谈的时候\N{\rEng}I guess that's about when I first noticed he was talking to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他受了什么样的伤?\N{\rEng}What sort of injury did he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,肩膀脱臼\N{\rEng}He dislocated his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么会受这样的伤?\N{\rEng}How did he manage to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是 嗯 那样的一些事 你知道的\N{\rEng}It was just one of those things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是意外事故\N{\rEng}Purely an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫喝醉...\N{\rEng}My husband had been drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然后比往常迟三个小时回到家\N{\rEng}...and he came home about three hours late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他那天晚上 心情不太好\N{\rEng}So he wasn't exactly in the greatest mood that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后丹尼把他一些教学用试卷 扔到满屋都是...\N{\rEng}And Danny had scattered some of his school papers all over the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我丈夫就拉住他的肩膀 想让他离开那些试卷\N{\rEng}...and my husband grabbed his arm to pull him away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样一些行为 你起码对孩子做过上百次...\N{\rEng}It's just the sort of thing you do 100 times with a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 平常在公园或者街道上\N{\rEng}...you know, in a park or in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当时有点失控...\N{\rEng}But on this particular occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫用力过猛\N{\rEng}...my husband just used too much strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他伤着了丹尼的肩膀\N{\rEng}...and he injured Danny's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 负面的事也有一些正面意义 因为他说...\N{\rEng}Anyway, something good did come out of it all because he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"温蒂 我绝对不会再犯同样的傻事\N{\rEng}..."Wendy, I'm never going to touch another drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,假如再发生的话 你可以离开我"\N{\rEng}And if I do, you can leave me."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 他的确做到了\N{\rEng}And he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他五个月没再沾过一点酒精\N{\rEng}He hasn't had any alcohol in 5 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,旅馆歇业日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们肯定到了很高的地方 空气都不太一样了\N{\rEng}We must really be high up. The air feels so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸?\N{\rEng}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了\N{\rEng}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该吃了早餐的\N{\rEng}You should've eaten your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们到了旅馆就给你找些吃的\N{\rEng}We'll get you something as soon as we get to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 妈妈\N{\rEng}Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在这附近 多纳组织被雪给困住的吧?\N{\rEng}Wasn't it around here that the Donner party got snowbound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为是在更西边的地方 在山脊地带\N{\rEng}I think that was farther west, in the Sierras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是多纳组织?\N{\rEng}What was the Donner party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是一个蓬车时代的殖民组织\N{\rEng}They were a party of settlers in covered wagon times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,某个冬天他们被雪困在山里头\N{\rEng}They got snowbound one winter in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,导致后来他们相互残杀当作食物 为的是让自己能够生存下来\N{\rEng}They had to resort to cannibalism in order to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是他们相互吃掉别人?\N{\rEng}You mean they ate each other up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为了活命 他们不得不这样做\N{\rEng}They had to, in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心 妈妈\N{\rEng}Don't worry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道人吃人的 在电视上看过\N{\rEng}I know all about cannibalism. I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看 我说没什么吧\N{\rEng}See, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他在电视上都看过了\N{\rEng}He saw it on the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飞机什么时候起飞? - 8点30分\N{\rEng}- What time does the plane leave? - 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就有充足的时间 可以仔细检查每样东西\N{\rEng}That gives us plenty of time to go over everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见 尤尔曼先生 - 再见\N{\rEng}- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 希望没有让你等太久\N{\rEng}Good morning. I hope you haven't been waiting too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我们正好有足够的时间去找点吃的\N{\rEng}No problem. We had time to grab a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很幸运 你能赶在他们关掉厨房前这样做\N{\rEng}Good. Glad you made it before they shut down the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家人都有四处看看吗?\N{\rEng}Is your family having a look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 因为我儿子发现了游戏室\N{\rEng}No, my son's discovered the games room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的行李都带来了吗? - 都在这儿\N{\rEng}- Has your luggage been brought in? - Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,预见到我们今天要做的一切...\N{\rEng}In view of all we have to cover today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议我们去看看你的住所 马上去\N{\rEng}...I suggest we have a quick look at your apartment and get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把特朗斯先生全家的行李 搬到他们的住所去\N{\rEng}Have the Torrances' things brought to their apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好先叫上我的家人\N{\rEng}I'd better collect my family first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的休闲室\N{\rEng}This is our Colorado Lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\rEng}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天!\N{\rEng}My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方实在太不可思议了 不是吗 亲爱的?\N{\rEng}This place is fantastic, isn't it, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是\N{\rEng}It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过这样的东西\N{\rEng}I've never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些全部是正统印地安风格吗?\N{\rEng}Are all these lndian designs authentic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信它们是主要是...\N{\rEng}I believe they're based...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,基于纳瓦霍和阿帕契部族的风格\N{\rEng}...mainly on Navajo and Apache motifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它们真是非常的华丽\N{\rEng}They're really gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上...\N{\rEng}As a matter of fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是我所见过的最华丽的旅馆了\N{\rEng}...this is probably the most gorgeous hotel I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个古老的地方有一个辉煌的过去\N{\rEng}This old place has had an illustrious past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在全盛时期 乘喷射机旅行的富豪 都当这里是重要观光景点\N{\rEng}In its heyday, it was a stopping place for the jet setters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在喷射客机旅行流行以前\N{\rEng}...even before anybody knew what a jet set was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经有四位总统呆过\N{\rEng}We had four presidents who stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很多的影视明星\N{\rEng}Lots of movie stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,皇族呢?\N{\rEng}Royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所有最出色的人\N{\rEng}All the best people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是旅馆职员的宿舍\N{\rEng}This is the staff wing of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天里这里以外的房间都没有暖气\N{\rEng}None of the other bedrooms are heated during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见 尤尔曼先生 - 再见 姑娘们\N{\rEng}- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Goodbye, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里便是你们的居室\N{\rEng}And here are your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,客厅 卧室 浴室\N{\rEng}Living room, bedroom, bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一间小房间 给你的儿子住\N{\rEng}And a small bedroom for your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对孩子而言 这相当不错\N{\rEng}Perfect for a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这里什么东西都很齐全\N{\rEng}Well, then. Place is very nicely self-contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比较好管理\N{\rEng}Easy to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒适\N{\rEng}Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 对一个家庭而言 非常舒适\N{\rEng}Yes, very cozy for a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你们想继续的话...\N{\rEng}If you feel like spreading out...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 你们还得去看看其它的那些地方\N{\rEng}...you have the rest of the hotel to move around in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这里非常的...\N{\rEng}Well, it's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有家的感觉\N{\rEng}...homey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们著名的树篱迷宫\N{\rEng}This is our famous hedge maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是非常有吸引力的所在 墙高是13英尺\N{\rEng}It's quite an attraction here. The walls are 13 feet high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这些树篱 它们就像这个旅馆一样历史悠久\N{\rEng}...and the hedge is as old as the hotel itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,非常有趣 不过 我绝对不想走进去...\N{\rEng}A lot of fun, but I wouldn't want to go in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我自己有把握 一个小时内能走出来\N{\rEng}...unless I had an hour to spare to find my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,遥望旅馆是什么时候修建的?\N{\rEng}When was the Overlook built?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,1907年开始建造\N{\rEng}Construction started in 1907.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,1909年竣工\N{\rEng}It was finished in 1909.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,地基据说是印地安人的墓地\N{\rEng}The site's supposed to be on an lndian burial ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这一度激怒了他们...\N{\rEng}They actually had to repel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在修建过程中 遭遇过印地安人的攻击\N{\rEng}...a few lndian attacks as they were building it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的雪地车\N{\rEng}That's our Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个都会开吧?\N{\rEng}Can you both drive a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 一般说来 开雪地车就跟开普通车辆没两样\N{\rEng}That's fine. Basically the Snowcat operates very much like a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会花太多时间来掌握它的\N{\rEng}It won't take you long to get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我们曾经从芝加哥找了个漆匠...\N{\rEng}As a matter of fact, we brought a decorator in from Chicago...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就在去年 重新粉刷旅馆的这个部分\N{\rEng}...just last year to refurbish this part of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他的确做的非常漂亮\N{\rEng}He sure did a beautiful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,粉红和金色是我最喜欢的色彩\N{\rEng}Pink and gold are my favorite colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的黄金舞厅\N{\rEng}This is our Gold Ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哇塞!\N{\rEng}I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以让300人在这里舒适地聚会\N{\rEng}We can accommodate up to 300 people here very comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 我们可以在这里开个精采的派对\N{\rEng}Boy, we could really have a good party in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.67,0:24:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕 在你获得补给品之前 此处也不真能让你开个好派对\N{\rEng}I'm afraid you won't do too well here unless you brought supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.67,0:24:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在关闭前 我们会把酒从柜台那边移走\N{\rEng}We remove the booze from the premises when we shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这将减低我们的保险费用\N{\rEng}That reduces the insurance we normally have to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.21,0:24:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不喝酒\N{\rEng}We don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你们非常幸运\N{\rEng}Then you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.02,0:24:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克 过来跟特朗斯太太和先生问个好\N{\rEng}Dick, come on over and say hello to Mr. and Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.45,0:24:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是迪克·哈罗朗 我们的首席厨师\N{\rEng}This is Dick Hallorann, our head chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗朗先生 我是杰克 这是我的妻子 温妮芙瑞德\N{\rEng}Mr. Hallorann, I'm Jack. This is my wife, Winifred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.73,0:24:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你\N{\rEng}Glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,特朗斯一家人 将在这个冬季照顾遥望旅馆\N{\rEng}The Torrances will take care of the Overlook this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.20,0:24:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这很好啊 你们对我们的旅馆印象如何?\N{\rEng}That's just great. How do you folks like our hotel so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.14,0:24:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,非常棒的地方\N{\rEng}It's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.21,0:24:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 丹尼!\N{\rEng}Hi, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚好在外面遇上他 他在找你们\N{\rEng}I found him outside looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.55,0:25:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经厌倦玩游戏了?\N{\rEng}Did you get tired of bombing the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.82,0:25:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来\N{\rEng}Come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.52,0:25:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 苏西\N{\rEng}Thank you, Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.89,0:25:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该带特朗斯太太去看一下厨房\N{\rEng}I think it'd be good if you could show Mrs. Torrance the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.10,0:25:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我和杰克可以继续逛逛\N{\rEng}...while I continue on with Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.16,0:25:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的荣幸 请这边走\N{\rEng}It would be a pleasure. Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 一会见 亲爱的\N{\rEng}Great. See you later, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.57,0:25:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 亲爱的\N{\rEng}Bye, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.31,0:25:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,特朗斯太太 你丈夫介绍你说名字叫温妮芙瑞德\N{\rEng}Mrs. Torrance, your husband introduced you as Winifred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.84,0:25:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 是叫你"温妮"还是"芙瑞蒂"?\N{\rEng}Now, are you a "Winnie", or a "Freddie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.58,0:25:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我温蒂\N{\rEng}I'm a Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.05,0:25:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂 不错 非常好的称呼\N{\rEng}Wendy. That's nice. That's the prettiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.45,0:25:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是厨房吗?\N{\rEng}This is the kitchen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.29,0:25:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.09,0:25:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这里吗 丹尼? 对你而言 这里够大了吗?\N{\rEng}How do you like it, Danny? is it big enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.86,0:25:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我见过的最大的地方\N{\rEng}It's the biggest place I ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.30,0:25:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这整个地方就像个巨大的迷宫\N{\rEng}This whole place is such an enormous maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.83,0:25:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我每次进来都得撒些面包屑做标记\N{\rEng}I'll have to leave a trail of breadcrumbs every time I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.31,0:25:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让它把你吓倒了\N{\rEng}Don't let it get you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.38,0:25:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它是很大 不过无论怎样也只是间厨房而已\N{\rEng}It's big, but it ain't nothing but a kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.08,0:25:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这里许多东西你都没必要去碰\N{\rEng}A lot of this stuff you'll never have to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.48,0:26:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果乱碰 我将很难收拾\N{\rEng}I wouldn't know what to do with it if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.92,0:26:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有一件事是肯定的 你不要担心没有食物\N{\rEng}One thing for sure, you don't have to worry about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.25,0:26:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,足够你们在这儿吃一年 而且保证每次的菜单都不一样\N{\rEng}You folks could eat here for a year and never have the same menu twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.13,0:26:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的冷藏室\N{\rEng}Right here is our walk-in freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.36,0:26:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里存放肉类\N{\rEng}This is where we keep all of our meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.64,0:26:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有15块烘干的排骨...\N{\rEng}You got 15 rib roasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.84,0:26:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,30袋汉堡 每袋10磅...\N{\rEng}...30 ten-pound bags of hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.17,0:26:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有12只火鸡 大约40只鸡...\N{\rEng}We got 12 turkeys, about 40 chickens...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.44,0:26:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,50份牛排 2打猪排...\N{\rEng}...50 sirloin steaks, two dozen of pork roast...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.75,0:26:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还有20条羔羊腿 你喜欢羔羊吧 多克?\N{\rEng}...and 20 legs of lamb. Do you like lamb, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.95,0:26:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢? 那 你最喜欢的是什么食物呢?\N{\rEng}You don't? What's your favorite food, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,法国油炸食物和调味酱\N{\rEng}French fries and ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.13,0:26:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们也能找到那个的 多克\N{\rEng}I think we can manage that too, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走 小心你们的脚下\N{\rEng}Come along, now. Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.81,0:26:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们叫他多克?\N{\rEng}How'd you know we call him Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.57,0:26:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么意思? - 多克 你叫了丹尼两次"多克"\N{\rEng}- Beg your pardon? - Doc. You called Danny "Doc" twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.81,0:26:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我有吗?\N{\rEng}I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.02,0:27:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有时叫他多克 就像卡通片 "疯狂的兔子" 里一样\N{\rEng}We call him Doc sometimes, like in the Bugs Bunny cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.35,0:27:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你是怎么知道的呢?\N{\rEng}But how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.82,0:27:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 我可能是听到你这么叫他了\N{\rEng}I guess I probably heard you call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.56,0:27:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能 但是我真的不记得...\N{\rEng}It's possible. But I honestly don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.03,0:27:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们见面后我有这么叫过他\N{\rEng}...calling him that since we've been with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.43,0:27:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 他看起来就像是多克 不是么?\N{\rEng}Anyway, he looks like a Doc, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.07,0:27:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 多克?\N{\rEng}What's up, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.34,0:27:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这里是储藏室\N{\rEng}Now, this is the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.28,0:27:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里我们存放...\N{\rEng}In here is where we keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.31,0:27:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的干料和罐头\N{\rEng}...all the dried goods and the canned goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.31,0:27:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有罐装的水果和蔬菜...\N{\rEng}We got canned fruits and vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.95,0:27:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,罐装的鱼和肉食 还有其它一些粮食\N{\rEng}...canned fish and meats, hot and cold cereals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,比如面包片 薯片 甜点...\N{\rEng}Post Toasties, Corn Flakes, Sugar Puffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.36,0:27:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爆米花 麦片 还有小麦油\N{\rEng}...Rice Krispies, oatmeal, Wheatena and Cream of Wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.63,0:27:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有成打的黑枫糖...\N{\rEng}You got a dozen jugs of black molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.27,0:27:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,60箱牛奶...\N{\rEng}We got 60 boxes of dried milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.11,0:27:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要些冰淇淋吗 多克?\N{\rEng}How'd you like some ice cream, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.99,0:27:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,各种小吃 甜点...\N{\rEng}Sociables, finger rolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.19,0:28:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要的每种食物\N{\rEng}...and 7 kinds of what have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.92,0:28:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我们有桃干 杏干...\N{\rEng}Now, we've got dried peaches, dried apricots...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.66,0:28:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...葡萄干和李干\N{\rEng}...dried raisins and dried prunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.96,0:28:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 如果你想快乐一点 你必须要保持秩序\N{\rEng}You know, you got to keep regular if you want to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.17,0:28:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们进行得怎样? - 很好\N{\rEng}- How're you getting on? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.01,0:28:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,能借用一下特朗斯太太吗? 我们正打算去地下室\N{\rEng}Can we borrow Mrs. Torrance? We're on our way to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.78,0:28:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证不会占用很长时间的\N{\rEng}I promise we won't keep her very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.92,0:28:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 尤尔曼先生 我正打算去做冰淇淋的\N{\rEng}No problem, Mr.Ullman. I was just getting to the ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.32,0:28:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢冰淇淋吧 多克?\N{\rEng}You like ice cream, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.06,0:28:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你喜欢呢\N{\rEng}I thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.22,0:28:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们介意在等你们的这段时间 我给丹尼一些冰淇淋么?\N{\rEng}You folks mind if I give Danny some ice cream while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.49,0:28:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然不会 - 我们不介意的\N{\rEng}- Not at all. - We don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.53,0:28:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 听到这个你很高兴吧 多克?\N{\rEng}- Good. - Sound good to you, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.93,0:28:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们去做你们的\N{\rEng}Okay, you behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.01,0:28:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要哪种冰淇淋呢?\N{\rEng}What kind of ice cream do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力\N{\rEng}Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是巧克力的 来吧 孩子 过来\N{\rEng}Chocolate it shall be. Come on, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.72,0:28:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是非常神奇的一天\N{\rEng}It's amazing, all this activity today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.92,0:28:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,客人和部分职员昨天就走了 但是...\N{\rEng}The guests and some staff left yesterday, but the...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.93,0:29:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这最后一天仍然是令人兴奋的\N{\rEng}...last day's always hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.56,0:29:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都想尽早上路\N{\rEng}Everybody wants to be on their way as early as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚5点后 就很难想像 这个地方有很多人在的样子\N{\rEng}By 5:00 tonight, you'll never know anybody was ever here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.07,0:29:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像艘鬼船一样 不是吗?\N{\rEng}Just like a ghost ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.81,0:29:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你晓得为什么 我知道你的名字叫多克吗?\N{\rEng}Do you know how I knew your name was Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白我在说什么吧?\N{\rEng}You know what I'm talking about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.73,0:29:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得 在我还小的时候...\N{\rEng}I can remember when I was a little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.64,0:29:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...我的祖母和我可以...\N{\rEng}...my grandmother and I could hold conversations...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.37,0:29:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...完全不开口进行交谈\N{\rEng}...entirely without ever opening our mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.28,0:29:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她管这叫"闪灵"\N{\rEng}She called it "shining."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来 我都认为只有我和她...\N{\rEng}And for a long time I thought it was just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.02,0:29:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有"闪灵"\N{\rEng}...that had "the shine" to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.26,0:30:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你也可能 一直认为自己有独特天赋一样\N{\rEng}Just like you probably thought you was the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.93,0:30:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 还有其他人也是一样的...\N{\rEng}But there are other folks...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他们大多数都没有体会到 甚至不相信\N{\rEng}...though mostly they don't know it, or don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.41,0:30:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你能这样已经多久了?\N{\rEng}How long have you been able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.05,0:30:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不想谈谈它呢?\N{\rEng}Why don't you want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该那样\N{\rEng}I'm not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.33,0:30:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说你不该那样?\N{\rEng}Who says you ain't supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.30,0:30:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼\N{\rEng}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.67,0:30:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是托尼?\N{\rEng}Who's Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.81,0:30:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是住在我嘴里的小男孩\N{\rEng}Tony's the little boy that lives in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.15,0:30:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼就是那个...\N{\rEng}Is Tony the one that...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.39,0:30:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你古怪事情的人?\N{\rEng}...tells you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.50,0:30:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎样告诉你的?\N{\rEng}How does he tell you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.70,0:31:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我就像是睡着了一样 然后 他就给我看一些东西\N{\rEng}It's like I go to sleep, and he shows me things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.21,0:31:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 当我醒来后 我就记不起来发生了什么\N{\rEng}But when I wake up, I can't remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.15,0:31:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母知道托尼的事吗?\N{\rEng}Does your mom and dad know about Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.35,0:31:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们知道 - 托尼有告诉你奇怪的事情吗?\N{\rEng}- Yes. - Do they know he tells you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.59,0:31:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 托尼叫我绝对不要和他们说\N{\rEng}No, Tony told me never to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.66,0:31:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼有告诉过你这个地方的事吗?\N{\rEng}Has Tony ever told you anything about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,关于遥望旅馆?\N{\rEng}About the Overlook Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.54,0:31:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想想 多克\N{\rEng}Now think real hard, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.55,0:31:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想想\N{\rEng}Think.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.69,0:31:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他似乎有给我看过一些东西\N{\rEng}Maybe he showed me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.36,0:31:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那 仔细想想是什么\N{\rEng}Try to think of what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.00,0:31:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗朗先生 你害怕这个地方吗?\N{\rEng}Mr. Hallorann, are you scared of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.40,0:32:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕 并不害怕\N{\rEng}No, Scared of nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.11,0:32:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只是...\N{\rEng}It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.34,0:32:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 一些地方 似乎就像人一样\N{\rEng}...you know, some places are like people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.01,0:32:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有的很特别...\N{\rEng}Some shine...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.92,0:32:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但 有的却相反\N{\rEng}...and some don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.55,0:32:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想遥望旅馆...\N{\rEng}I guess you could say the Overlook Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.89,0:32:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它有些东西 很特别 就像闪灵一样\N{\rEng}...has something about it that's like shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.23,0:32:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有发生过不好的事吗?\N{\rEng}Is there something bad here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.25,0:32:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 多克 一些事发生后...\N{\rEng}You know, Doc, when something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.88,0:32:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它总会留下一些痕迹\N{\rEng}...it can leave a trace of itself behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.29,0:32:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就像...\N{\rEng}Say, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.06,0:32:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大胡子会在胡须上留下面包屑\N{\rEng}...if someone burns toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.23,0:32:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 某些事情却留下不一样的痕迹\N{\rEng}Maybe things that happen leave other kind of traces behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.07,0:33:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是所有人都可以注意到的那种痕迹\N{\rEng}Not things that anyone can notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.71,0:33:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 拥有闪灵的人可以看到\N{\rEng}But things that people who shine can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.61,0:33:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他们能看到还没发生的事一样...\N{\rEng}Just like they can see things that haven't happened yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.19,0:33:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在某些时候 他们能看到许久以前发生的一些事\N{\rEng}...sometimes they can see things that happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.89,0:33:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 这里曾经发生过许多事...\N{\rEng}I think a lot of things happened right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.96,0:33:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在这所特别的旅馆的悠久历史里\N{\rEng}...in this particular hotel over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.20,0:33:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这些事 并不全都是好事\N{\rEng}And not all of them was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 237房发生过什么?\N{\rEng}What about room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.88,0:33:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,237房?\N{\rEng}Room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.39,0:33:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕237房 不是吗?\N{\rEng}You're scared of room 237, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕 我不害怕\N{\rEng}No, I ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.23,0:33:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗朗先生 237房里面到底有些什么?\N{\rEng}Mr. Hallorann, what is in room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.40,0:33:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.20,0:33:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,237房里面没有什么 根本没有!\N{\rEng}There ain't nothing in room 237.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.64,0:34:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 你也没有必要去那个地方\N{\rEng}But you ain't got no business going in there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.08,0:34:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不要靠近它\N{\rEng}So stay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.41,0:34:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗? 不要靠近它!\N{\rEng}You understand? Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.76,0:34:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.30,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨 亲爱的\N{\rEng}Good morning, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.04,0:35:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的早餐已经做好了\N{\rEng}Your breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.57,0:35:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在几点?\N{\rEng}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.41,0:35:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大概11点30分\N{\rEng}It's about 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.18,0:36:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEng}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.72,0:36:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们实在是睡得太晚\N{\rEng}I guess we've been staying up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.45,0:36:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.19,0:36:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,都按你喜欢的口味做的 尝尝吧\N{\rEng}I made them just the way you like them, sunny-side up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.36,0:36:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.20,0:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的风景真的很美\N{\rEng}It's really pretty outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.20,0:36:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完早餐后 我们可以出去散步么?\N{\rEng}How about taking me for a walk after you finish your breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.04,0:36:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我得先写些东西\N{\rEng}I suppose I ought to try to do some writing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.81,0:36:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么构思了吗?\N{\rEng}Any ideas yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.48,0:36:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太多的构思\N{\rEng}Lots of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.35,0:36:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是都没有好的\N{\rEng}No good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.35,0:36:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好创意总会有的\N{\rEng}Something will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.32,0:36:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是要养成每天都得写作的习惯\N{\rEng}It's just a matter of settling into the habit of writing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.83,0:36:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样而已\N{\rEng}That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.63,0:36:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,到这个地方来真是不错啊 不是吗?\N{\rEng}It's really nice up here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.34,0:36:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这儿\N{\rEng}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.27,0:36:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的喜欢\N{\rEng}I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.78,0:36:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有在别的地方 感觉有这么舒适和快活\N{\rEng}I've never been this happy or comfortable anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.01,0:36:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么快就能适应这样一个大地方 真是让人惊讶\N{\rEng}It's amazing how fast you get used to such a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.98,0:37:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 我们刚来的时候...\N{\rEng}I tell you, when we first came up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.09,0:37:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这里会非常可怕\N{\rEng}...I thought it was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.59,0:37:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我立刻就喜欢上了这儿\N{\rEng}I fell in love with it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.83,0:37:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当我来这里应聘的时候...\N{\rEng}When I came up here for my interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.00,0:37:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就感到 我似乎曾经来过这儿\N{\rEng}...it was as though I'd been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.04,0:37:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我们总会有些似曾相识的感觉...\N{\rEng}I mean, we all have moments of deja vu...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.87,0:37:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这次有些不一样\N{\rEng}...but this was ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.81,0:37:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎能知道...\N{\rEng}It was almost as though I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.48,0:37:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每个角落会有些什么东西存在\N{\rEng}...what was going to be around every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.75,0:38:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,输了的人就要打扫整个美国 怎样?\N{\rEng}The loser has to keep America clean. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.16,0:38:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 你已经要输了\N{\rEng}- All right. - And you're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.93,0:38:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要来抓你了 你最好跑快点!\N{\rEng}And I'm going to get you. You'd better run fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.07,0:38:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,注意了!\N{\rEng}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.41,0:38:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我快抓到你了\N{\rEng}I'm coming in close.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.48,0:38:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,输家要打扫整个美国哦\N{\rEng}Loser has to keep America clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.21,0:38:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要打扫整个美国\N{\rEng}Keep America clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.85,0:38:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼 你赢了\N{\rEng}Danny, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.65,0:38:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们休息会吧 走走\N{\rEng}Let's take the rest of this walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.52,0:38:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把手给我\N{\rEng}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.56,0:38:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很漂亮吧?\N{\rEng}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.12,0:38:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,死胡同\N{\rEng}Dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.95,0:39:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了\N{\rEng}We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.09,0:39:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧?\N{\rEng}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.02,0:40:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮\N{\rEng}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.42,0:40:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有想到它居然这么大 你呢?\N{\rEng}I didn't think it was going to be this big. Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.63,0:40:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.33,0:40:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.97,0:40:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟福在追查一起...\N{\rEng}Rutherford was serving a life sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.57,0:40:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在1968年执行枪决的命案\N{\rEng}...for a 1968 shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.54,0:40:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对在阿斯本失踪妇女的搜索 仍然持续进行着\N{\rEng}And the search continues for that missing Aspen woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.62,0:40:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊·罗伯逊 24岁 已经失踪10天了\N{\rEng}24-year-old Susan Robertson has been missing 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.19,0:40:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她在和丈夫一起的打猎途中走失\N{\rEng}She disappeared on a hunting trip with her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.12,0:40:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也许不得不取消搜索...\N{\rEng}They may have to call off the search...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.13,0:40:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,假如预测的暴风雪明天果真来临\N{\rEng}...if a predicted snowstorm moves in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.86,0:41:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,丹佛今天风和日丽...\N{\rEng}It's so beautiful in Denver today...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.93,0:41:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很难想像一场暴风雪就要来临\N{\rEng}...it's hard to believe a snowstorm could be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.27,0:41:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至想出去沐浴阳光...\N{\rEng}I want to go outside and lie in the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的北方和西方 天气仍然很冷 下着雪\N{\rEng}...yet to our north, to our west, it is snowing and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.04,0:41:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且冷空气在移动...\N{\rEng}And it's moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.44,0:41:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这同时 它正移向科罗拉多州 难以置信...\N{\rEng}...right here towards Colorado as we talk. It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.16,0:43:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 亲爱的\N{\rEng}Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.19,0:43:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,工作进行得怎样?\N{\rEng}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.17,0:43:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还行\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.44,0:43:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今天写了很多吗?\N{\rEng}Get a lot written today?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.70,0:44:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.05,0:44:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报说 今晚会开始下雪\N{\rEng}The weather forecast said it's going to snow tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样? 你想我怎样?\N{\rEng}What do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.29,0:44:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 亲爱的\N{\rEng}Come on, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这么不高兴吧\N{\rEng}Don't be so grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.23,0:44:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有...\N{\rEng}I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.93,0:44:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不高兴\N{\rEng}...being grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.34,0:44:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想完成我的工作\N{\rEng}I just want to finish my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.64,0:44:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我明白了\N{\rEng}Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.28,0:44:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿我给你带点三明治来\N{\rEng}I'll come back later with a couple of sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.08,0:44:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到那时候 你也许能让我看看 你已经写了些什么\N{\rEng}Maybe you'll let me read something then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.76,0:44:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂...\N{\rEng}Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.06,0:44:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...让我告诉你一件事\N{\rEng}...let me explain something to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.56,0:44:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当你进来打断我的时候 意味着你破坏了我的集中力\N{\rEng}When you come in and interrupt, you're breaking my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.63,0:44:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我的注意力转移开了...\N{\rEng}You're distracting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.27,0:44:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我得费力气 再把注意力摆回工作上去\N{\rEng}...and it will then take me time to get back to where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.91,0:44:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗?\N{\rEng}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.23,0:45:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.61,0:45:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.95,0:45:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得定个新规矩:\N{\rEng}We're going to make a new rule:
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.88,0:45:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么时候 只要我在这里...\N{\rEng}Whenever I'm in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.52,0:45:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你有听到我打字的声音...\N{\rEng}...and you hear me typing...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.59,0:45:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,或者 无论你听到我在这里干什么\N{\rEng}...or whatever the fuck you hear me doing in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.73,0:45:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我呆在这儿 就意味着我在工作\N{\rEng}...when I'm in here, that means I am working.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.23,0:45:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 那时不能进来打扰我\N{\rEng}That means don't come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你现在明白了吗?\N{\rEng}Now, do you think you can handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.18,0:45:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 好\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.74,0:45:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么还不行动 给我滚出这个地方?\N{\rEng}Why don't you start right now and get the fuck out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.42,0:45:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.33,0:46:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.99,0:46:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你好了吧!\N{\rEng}All right, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.79,0:46:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你手里面还有\N{\rEng}I know you've got more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.70,0:46:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没打中!\N{\rEng}Missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.34,0:46:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没了!\N{\rEng}Don't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.41,0:46:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那不怕你了\N{\rEng}No fair anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.00,0:46:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.32,0:47:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该早想到\N{\rEng}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.89,0:48:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是KDK 12在呼叫KDK 1\N{\rEng}This is KDK 12 calling KDK 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.90,0:48:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 12 呼叫 KDK 1\N{\rEng}KDK 12 to KDK 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.80,0:48:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是KDK 1 我们收到你的呼叫了 完毕\N{\rEng}This is KDK 1. We're receiving you. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.31,0:48:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 我是遥望旅馆的温蒂·特朗斯\N{\rEng}Hi, this is Wendy Torrance at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.01,0:48:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你们在上头过得如何? 完毕\N{\rEng}Hi, how are you folks getting on up there? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.08,0:48:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们过得很好\N{\rEng}We're just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.62,0:48:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们的电话 似乎有点问题\N{\rEng}But our telephones aren't doing too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.29,0:48:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是线路断了吗? 完毕\N{\rEng}Are the lines down, by any chance? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.96,0:48:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 因为暴风雪的关系 一部分线路出问题了 完毕\N{\rEng}Yes, quite a few of them are down due to the storm. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.06,0:48:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能尽快修好吗? 完毕\N{\rEng}Any chance of them being repaired soon? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.47,0:48:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我恐怕不行\N{\rEng}Well, I wouldn't like to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.83,0:48:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可能整个冬天都只能这样 得等到春天才会修理 完毕\N{\rEng}Most winters they stay that way until spring. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.77,0:48:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 这暴风雪可真是厉害 不是吗? 完毕\N{\rEng}Boy, this storm is really something, isn't it? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.64,0:48:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 真是如此\N{\rEng}Yes. It's one of the worst we've had for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.11,0:48:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还能为你做点其它的什么吗? 特朗斯太太 完毕\N{\rEng}Is there anything else we can do for you, Mrs. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.79,0:48:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 没什么了 完毕\N{\rEng}I suppose not. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.55,0:49:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你们遇到什么麻烦 就呼叫我们\N{\rEng}If you folks have any problems up there, just give us a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.06,0:49:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 特朗斯太太...\N{\rEng}And, Mrs. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.56,0:49:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们最好一直都开着无线通话装置\N{\rEng}It might be a good idea if you leave your radio on all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.60,0:49:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我们会这样做的\N{\rEng}Okay. We'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.30,0:49:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴能和你交谈\N{\rEng}It was real nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.57,0:49:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 挂断\N{\rEng}Bye. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.12,0:49:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 丹尼\N{\rEng}Hello, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.59,0:49:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来和我们一起玩吧\N{\rEng}Come and play with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.90,0:50:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们一起玩吧 丹尼\N{\rEng}Come and play with us, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.50,0:50:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,永远...\N{\rEng}Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.14,0:50:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,永远...\N{\rEng}...and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.85,0:50:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\rEng}...and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.35,0:50:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼...\N{\rEng}Tony...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.99,0:50:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕\N{\rEng}...I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.50,0:51:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,记住哈罗朗先生说过的话\N{\rEng}Remember what Mr. Hallorann said.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.67,0:51:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就像是书里的插画一样 没什么好怕的 丹尼\N{\rEng}It's just like pictures in a book, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.77,0:51:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那并不是真实的东西\N{\rEng}It isn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.87,0:51:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.11,0:51:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我给你些钱\N{\rEng}Please let me give you some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.14,0:51:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我想我不能接受\N{\rEng}I wouldn't think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.41,0:51:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 那你要我怎样报答你?\N{\rEng}Well, how can I repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.64,0:51:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 真的\N{\rEng}It's okay. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.18,0:51:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我想喝些咖啡\N{\rEng}Well, I'm going to have some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.48,0:51:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你也喝点好吗?\N{\rEng}Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.75,0:51:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.02,0:51:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 请坐\N{\rEng}Great. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.80,0:51:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,神奇炸圈饼 你自己拿罢\N{\rEng}Marvelous doughnuts. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.08,0:51:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咖啡马上就好 - 妈妈\N{\rEng}- Coffee will be ready in a few minutes. - Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.56,0:51:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.28,0:52:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去我的房间拿我的消防车吗?\N{\rEng}Can I go up to my room and get my fire engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.05,0:52:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不行 爸爸正在睡觉呢\N{\rEng}Not right now. Daddy's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.76,0:52:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我会小心不出声的\N{\rEng}I won't make any noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.33,0:52:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 多克\N{\rEng}Now come on, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.43,0:52:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸才睡了一会儿\N{\rEng}He only went to bed a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.34,0:52:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再等等么?\N{\rEng}Can't you wait till later?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.34,0:52:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会弄出声响的 我保证 我会掂脚尖走进去\N{\rEng}I won't make a sound. I promise I'll tiptoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.68,0:52:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.18,0:52:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真的不要弄出声音\N{\rEng}But really don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.78,0:52:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会的 妈妈\N{\rEng}I won't, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.08,0:52:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到就马上回来...\N{\rEng}Make sure you come right back...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.02,0:52:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我得马上去做午饭了\N{\rEng}...because I'm going to make lunch soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.16,0:52:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 妈妈\N{\rEng}Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.92,0:53:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去我的房间拿我的消防车吗?\N{\rEng}Can I go to my room and get my fire engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.83,0:53:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来\N{\rEng}Come here for a minute first.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.04,0:54:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎样呢 多克?\N{\rEng}How's it going, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.30,0:54:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.41,0:54:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,过得好吗?\N{\rEng}Having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.28,0:54:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 爸爸\N{\rEng}Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.66,0:54:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.09,0:54:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能过得愉快\N{\rEng}I want you to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.96,0:54:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我很愉快 爸爸\N{\rEng}I am, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.14,0:54:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸 - 什么?\N{\rEng}- Dad. - yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.04,0:54:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉不好?\N{\rEng}Do you feel bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.99,0:54:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 只是有些累\N{\rEng}No, I'm just a little bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.66,0:55:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那 你为什么不睡会呢?\N{\rEng}Then why don't you go to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.80,0:55:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能睡\N{\rEng}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.83,0:55:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为还有很多事得做\N{\rEng}I got too much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.45,0:55:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这所旅馆吗?\N{\rEng}Do you like this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.72,0:55:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.09,0:55:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢它\N{\rEng}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.63,0:55:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不是吗?\N{\rEng}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.34,0:55:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 我也是\N{\rEng}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.47,0:55:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.88,0:55:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能喜欢这里\N{\rEng}I want you to like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.19,0:55:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我们能永远待在这个地方...\N{\rEng}I wish we could stay here forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.79,0:55:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,永远...\N{\rEng}...and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.26,0:55:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\rEng}...and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.04,0:56:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.34,0:56:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远都不会伤害我和妈妈 对吗?\N{\rEng}You would never hurt Mommy or me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.91,0:56:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思?\N{\rEng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.52,0:56:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈对你说过些什么?\N{\rEng}Did your mother ever say that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.79,0:56:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,说我会伤害你?\N{\rEng}That I would hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.36,0:56:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 爸爸\N{\rEng}No, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.90,0:56:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?\N{\rEng}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.00,0:56:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 爸爸\N{\rEng}Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.38,0:56:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 丹尼\N{\rEng}I love you, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.61,0:56:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 胜过一切...\N{\rEng}I love you more than anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.42,0:56:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,胜过世上的任何东西...\N{\rEng}...in the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.75,0:56:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会伤害你的...\N{\rEng}...and I would never do anything to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.12,0:56:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\rEng}...never.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.23,0:56:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 不是吗?\N{\rEng}You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.76,0:56:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 爸爸\N{\rEng}Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.27,0:57:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.09,0:57:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.10,0:57:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rEng}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.29,0:58:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rEng}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.30,0:58:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你在吗?\N{\rEng}Mom, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.33,0:59:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.60,0:59:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的...\N{\rEng}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.70,0:59:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事?\N{\rEng}...what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.28,1:00:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我作梦了...\N{\rEng}I had the most...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.88,1:00:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,作一个我一生中最可怕的梦\N{\rEng}...terrible nightmare I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.42,1:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最最可怕的 - 好了 好了 现在没事了\N{\rEng}- It was the most horrible dream. - It's okay, it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.56,1:00:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\rEng}Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.20,1:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我梦见...\N{\rEng}I dreamed that I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.00,1:00:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了你和丹尼\N{\rEng}...that I killed you and Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.17,1:00:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我不仅仅是杀了你们\N{\rEng}But I didn't just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.71,1:00:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还把你们切成一片一片的\N{\rEng}I cut you up into little pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.15,1:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.39,1:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定是疯了\N{\rEng}I must be losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.22,1:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会没事的\N{\rEng}Everything's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.96,1:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 让我们站起来\N{\rEng}Come on. Let's get up off the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.51,1:00:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\rEng}There. Now sit up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.45,1:01:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.85,1:01:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,放松\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.36,1:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼!\N{\rEng}Danny!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.86,1:01:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事\N{\rEng}Everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.99,1:01:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的房间玩会儿\N{\rEng}Just go play in your room for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.50,1:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸有些头痛\N{\rEng}Your dad's just got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.87,1:01:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼 听到我说什么了吗? 去你房间里玩\N{\rEng}Danny, mind what I say. Go play in your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.87,1:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 等我把他带走\N{\rEng}Honey, let me just go get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.01,1:01:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回来\N{\rEng}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.45,1:01:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不听我的话?\N{\rEng}Why don't you mind me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.12,1:01:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.16,1:01:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你脖子上是怎么搞的?\N{\rEng}What happened to your neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.50,1:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你脖子上到底是怎么回事?\N{\rEng}What happened to your neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.60,1:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他这样的...\N{\rEng}You did this to him...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.00,1:02:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你吗?\N{\rEng}...didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.27,1:02:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个狗娘养的\N{\rEng}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.54,1:02:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然这样对他!\N{\rEng}You did this to him!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.61,1:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然? !\N{\rEng}Didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.38,1:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可以这样? !\N{\rEng}How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.29,1:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么忍心? !\N{\rEng}How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.89,1:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我得来点喝的 无论要我付出什么代价\N{\rEng}God! I'd give anything for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.63,1:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,即便付出我该死的灵魂...\N{\rEng}I'd give my goddamn soul...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.74,1:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能换来一杯啤酒\N{\rEng}...for just a glass of beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.22,1:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 罗伊德\N{\rEng}Hi, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.26,1:04:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚似乎没什么人 不是吗?\N{\rEng}A little slow tonight, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.54,1:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Yes it is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.88,1:04:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想要点什么?\N{\rEng}What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.01,1:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题你问得好 罗伊德...\N{\rEng}I'm awfully glad you asked me that, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.18,1:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我正好有两张20块\N{\rEng}...because I just happen to have two twenties...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.72,1:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和两张10块的钞票摆在我口袋里\N{\rEng}...and two tens right here in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.82,1:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我正担心 它们会在口袋里待到下个春天呢\N{\rEng}I was afraid they were going to be there until next April.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.80,1:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好 听着 我要的是:\N{\rEng}So here's what:
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.93,1:05:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我一瓶波本...\N{\rEng}You slip me a bottle of bourbon...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.44,1:05:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个装了冰块的杯子\N{\rEng}...a little glass and some ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.44,1:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吧 不是吗 罗伊德?\N{\rEng}You can do that, can't you, Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.91,1:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不很忙 是吧?\N{\rEng}You're not too busy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.85,1:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生 我一点都不忙\N{\rEng}No, sir. I'm not busy at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.85,1:05:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好伙计\N{\rEng}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.72,1:05:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它们摆好...\N{\rEng}You set them up...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.09,1:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把它们各个击破\N{\rEng}...and I'll knock them back, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.09,1:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,白人的使命 罗伊德 我的伙计\N{\rEng}White man's burden, Lloyd, my man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.23,1:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,白人的使命 (暗指: 击退印地安人)\N{\rEng}White man's burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.47,1:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 罗伊德...\N{\rEng}Say, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.81,1:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像一时有点轻飘飘了\N{\rEng}...it seems I'm temporarily light.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.91,1:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 我在这边信誉如何?\N{\rEng}How's my credit in this joint, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.61,1:05:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的信誉很好 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Your credit's fine, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.68,1:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以发誓\N{\rEng}That's swell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.52,1:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我欣赏你 罗伊德\N{\rEng}I like you, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.42,1:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都欣赏你\N{\rEng}I always liked you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.29,1:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是其中最优秀的\N{\rEng}You were always the best of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.83,1:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好得不能再好的吧台招待...\N{\rEng}Best goddamned bartender...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.39,1:06:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,从蒂姆布克图到缅因州的波特兰\N{\rEng}...from Timbuktu to Portland, Maine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.53,1:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或是到俄勒冈州的波特兰 都是一样的\N{\rEng}Or Portland, Oregon, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.03,1:06:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖\N{\rEng}Thank you for saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.14,1:06:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在货车上过了备受煎熬的5个月...\N{\rEng}Here's to 5 miserable months on the wagon...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.88,1:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,给我带来了永久的心灵创伤\N{\rEng}...and all the irreparable harm that it's caused me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.17,1:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,过得还顺利吧? 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}How are things going, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.98,1:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,情况会好转的\N{\rEng}Things could be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.08,1:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,情况会整个彻底好转的\N{\rEng}Things could be a whole lot better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.72,1:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望没什么太大问题\N{\rEng}I hope it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.06,1:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么大问题啦\N{\rEng}Nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.69,1:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只是跟楼上的哪个老精子银行(注:温蒂) 有点小小问题\N{\rEng}Just a little problem with...the old sperm bank upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.80,1:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但我完全可以掌握\N{\rEng}Nothing I can't handle, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.37,1:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.54,1:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,女人\N{\rEng}Women.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.74,1:07:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能够和她们一起生活...\N{\rEng}Can't live with them...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.48,1:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,离开她们又活不下去\N{\rEng}...can't live without them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.52,1:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,智慧金言 罗伊德\N{\rEng}Words of wisdom, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.29,1:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,智慧...\N{\rEng}Words of...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.95,1:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,良言\N{\rEng}...wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.00,1:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝没有碰他 妈的\N{\rEng}I never laid a hand on him, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.44,1:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEng}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.11,1:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,连一根寒毛都没去碰\N{\rEng}I wouldn't touch one hair on his goddamn little head.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.32,1:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱那个小王八蛋\N{\rEng}I love the little son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.06,1:07:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我会为他做任何事\N{\rEng}I'd do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.09,1:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的任何事情\N{\rEng}Any fucking thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.97,1:08:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但那个婊子!\N{\rEng}But that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.54,1:08:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我还活着...\N{\rEng}As long as I live...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.51,1:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她就不会让我忘记发生过的事\N{\rEng}...she'll never let me forget what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.52,1:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实伤害过他一次 好不好?\N{\rEng}I did hurt him once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.73,1:08:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,单纯的意外\N{\rEng}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.10,1:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不算故意的\N{\rEng}Completely unintentional.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.97,1:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人遇到那种事 都可能那样反应\N{\rEng}It could have happened to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.94,1:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 他妈的 都过去三个年头了!\N{\rEng}And it was three goddamn years ago!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.61,1:08:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那小杂碎把我的稿纸扔满地\N{\rEng}The little fucker had thrown all my papers all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.65,1:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想把他拉起来\N{\rEng}All I tried to do was pull him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.89,1:08:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一时肌肉动作失去协调\N{\rEng}A momentary loss of muscular coordination.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.89,1:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...\N{\rEng}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.66,1:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,力道多出几磅...\N{\rEng}...a few extra foot-pounds of energy...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.40,1:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,平均每秒 每秒才...\N{\rEng}...per second, per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.35,1:09:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝你在这里\N{\rEng}Thank God you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.49,1:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,旅馆里除了我们 还有另一个人在\N{\rEng}There's someone else in the hotel with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.90,1:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一间房子里有个疯女人\N{\rEng}There's a crazy woman in one of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.63,1:09:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她想把丹尼掐死\N{\rEng}She tried to strangle Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.74,1:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的神智不清了?\N{\rEng}Are you out of your fucking mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.08,1:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是真的 真的!\N{\rEng}It's the truth! Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.31,1:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓 丹尼告诉我的\N{\rEng}I swear it. Danny told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.65,1:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他上去 进入其中一间卧房\N{\rEng}He went up into one of the bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.72,1:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,门是开着的 他看见这疯女人在浴缸里\N{\rEng}The door was open, and he saw this crazy woman in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.39,1:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她想把他掐死!\N{\rEng}She tried to strangle him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.43,1:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪个房间?\N{\rEng}Which room was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.84,1:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,来自迈阿密的10频道\N{\rEng}From Channel 10 in Miami...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.18,1:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是新闻观察和格兰林克...\N{\rEng}...this is Newswatch with Glen Rinker...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.75,1:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,安毕雪与广受好评的新闻观察小组\N{\rEng}...Ann Bishop, and the award- winning Newswatch team.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.28,1:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 我是10频道新闻观察的格兰林克\N{\rEng}Good evening. I'm Glen Rinker, Newswatch Ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.92,1:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当迈阿密闷热的天气持续刷新记录 冬季的热浪...\N{\rEng}As Miami continues to swelter in a record winter heat wave...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.26,1:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,带来超过华氏90度的高温...\N{\rEng}...bringing temperatures to the 90s...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.59,1:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,中部和山区的州区 却被埋在皑皑白雪之中\N{\rEng}...Central and Mountain states are buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.93,1:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚光是科罗拉多 几个小时内就积了10英吋厚的雪\N{\rEng}In Colorado, 10 inches of snow fell injust a few hours tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.14,1:10:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎不可能在洛矶山脉从事旅游活动\N{\rEng}Travel in the Rockies is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.57,1:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,机场被迫关闭 滞留了成千上万的旅客\N{\rEng}Airports are shut down, stranding thousands of passengers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.74,1:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,高速公路被雪堆阻挡\N{\rEng}Highways are blocked by snowdrifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.84,1:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,铁轨被冻住\N{\rEng}Railroad tracks are frozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.81,1:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多官方告知新闻观察...\N{\rEng}Officials in Colorado tell Newswatch...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.05,1:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,已经至少有三个人在寒风中被冻死\N{\rEng}...at least 3 have been killed by exposure to freezing winds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.82,1:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,希望科罗拉多政府...\N{\rEng}The governor of Colorado is expected...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.32,1:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,宣布进入天气警戒状态\N{\rEng}...to declare a weather emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.26,1:10:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,应动员全民进行防备...\N{\rEng}The National Guard might be called out...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.30,1:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,清除街道和公路积雪\N{\rEng}...to clear streets and roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.70,1:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报 今晚到明天...\N{\rEng}Weather forecasters predict more snow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.13,1:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,将有更多的降雪 并伴有强风...\N{\rEng}...and heavy winds tonight and tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.34,1:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,同时温度会降到0度以下\N{\rEng}...with temperatures dropping well below zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.17,1:10:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回到佛罗里达 我们碰到了相反的问题\N{\rEng}Back here in Florida, we've got the opposite problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.38,1:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,炎热和潮湿预计会更加恶化\N{\rEng}The heat and humidity are supposed to climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.81,1:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,应该封锁本地的沙滩\N{\rEng}Local beaches should bejammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.98,1:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的气象专家华特克朗斯...\N{\rEng}Our weather expert, Walter Cronice...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.22,1:11:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,将在稍后的新闻观察里 为您播报本地天气预报\N{\rEng}...will have the local forecast later on Newswatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.17,1:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 您所拨的号码无法接通\N{\rEng}We're sorry. Your call cannot be completed as dialed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.15,1:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您需要帮助请拨叫接线员\N{\rEng}If you need assistance, please call the operator.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.24,1:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰克? - 是 是我\N{\rEng}- Jack? - Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.57,1:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\N{\rEng}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.68,1:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到什么了吗?\N{\rEng}Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.65,1:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 什么也没有\N{\rEng}No. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.99,1:17:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么见鬼的东西都没看到\N{\rEng}I didn't see one goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.89,1:17:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了丹尼说的那间房了吗? 去237?\N{\rEng}You went into the room Danny said? To 237?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.60,1:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我去了\N{\rEng}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.63,1:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么也没看到?\N{\rEng}And you didn't see anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.64,1:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没有\N{\rEng}Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.84,1:17:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样了?\N{\rEng}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.31,1:17:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在睡\N{\rEng}He's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.51,1:17:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.45,1:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定明天早上 他就会回过神来的\N{\rEng}I'm sure he'll be himself again in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.03,1:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定就是那个房间吗?\N{\rEng}Are you sure it was the right room?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.73,1:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 也许丹尼弄错了\N{\rEng}I mean, maybe Danny made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.10,1:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定就是进去那个房间\N{\rEng}He must have gone in that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.67,1:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,门开着 灯也亮着\N{\rEng}The door was open, the lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.98,1:18:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是弄不明白\N{\rEng}I just don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.65,1:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他脖子上的伤痕是怎么回事?\N{\rEng}What about those bruises on his neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.86,1:18:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把他弄成那样的\N{\rEng}Somebody did that to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.47,1:18:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是...\N{\rEng}I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.57,1:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己弄的\N{\rEng}...he did it to himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.15,1:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.05,1:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可能\N{\rEng}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.39,1:18:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你排除他对所发生的事情的说法...\N{\rEng}Once you rule out his version of what happened...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.30,1:18:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就再没有其他解释了\N{\rEng}...there is no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.37,1:18:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗?\N{\rEng}Is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.07,1:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那和我们来这里前的那次事件...\N{\rEng}It wouldn't be that different from the episode...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.18,1:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么不同的\N{\rEng}...that he had before we came up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.75,1:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗?\N{\rEng}Would it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.89,1:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么原因...\N{\rEng}Whatever the explanation is...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.33,1:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们...\N{\rEng}...I think we...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.93,1:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,得带丹尼离开这里\N{\rEng}...have to get Danny out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.44,1:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,带他离开这里?\N{\rEng}Get him out of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.45,1:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是...\N{\rEng}You mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.22,1:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这座旅馆?\N{\rEng}...just leave the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.17,1:19:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,制造一个像这样的问题...\N{\rEng}It is so...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.83,1:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是你的风格\N{\rEng}...typical of you to create a problem like this...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.47,1:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当我总算有机会完成什么的时候!\N{\rEng}...when I finally have a chance to accomplish something!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.21,1:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当我真正投入我的作品的时候!\N{\rEng}When I'm really into my work!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.98,1:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在回去 我真的能写出自己的大作 不是吗?\N{\rEng}I could really write my own ticket if I went back now, couldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.15,1:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,铲铲车道 洗洗车子\N{\rEng}Shoveling out driveways, work in a car wash.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.09,1:20:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这类事情很吸引你?\N{\rEng}Any of that appeal to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.39,1:20:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,到现在我一直让你糟蹋我的生活...\N{\rEng}I have let you fuck up my life so far...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.29,1:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我不会再让你糟蹋了\N{\rEng}...but I am not going to let you fuck this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.86,1:21:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 森林服务台\N{\rEng}Good evening. Forest Service.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.73,1:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫迪克·霍洛朗\N{\rEng}My name is Dick Hallorann.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.36,1:21:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是遥望旅馆的厨师长\N{\rEng}I'm the head chef at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.00,1:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 有什么我能为您效劳吗?\N{\rEng}Good evening. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.33,1:21:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想打个电话到那上面去 很急...\N{\rEng}I've been trying to make an urgent phone call up there...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.10,1:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但接线员告诉我线路不通\N{\rEng}...but the operator said that the phone lines are down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.61,1:21:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这周围的很多线路在暴风雪里都断掉了\N{\rEng}A lot of lines around here are down due to the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.41,1:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想给您带来任何麻烦...\N{\rEng}I hate to put you through any trouble...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.28,1:22:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在有一家人孤零零的在上头 还带着个小孩子\N{\rEng}...but there's a family up there all by themselves with a young kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.72,1:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,又遇到了这场暴风雪 总之...\N{\rEng}And with this storm and everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.59,1:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您能用无线电联系上他们的话 我会非常感激的...\N{\rEng}...I'd appreciate it if you'd give them a call on your radio...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.69,1:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想看看是不是一切正常\N{\rEng}...just to see if everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.20,1:22:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意这么做\N{\rEng}I'll be glad to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.70,1:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不20分钟后再打给我呢?\N{\rEng}Why don't you call me back in about 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.70,1:22:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 我会那样做的\N{\rEng}Thank you very much. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.94,1:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先生\N{\rEng}All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.69,1:22:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Good evening, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.86,1:22:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEng}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.89,1:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 罗伊德\N{\rEng}Hi, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.56,1:23:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,离开了一阵子 但现在我又回来了\N{\rEng}Been away, but now I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.70,1:23:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Good evening, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.10,1:23:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真好\N{\rEng}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.30,1:23:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回来真不错 罗伊德\N{\rEng}It's good to be back, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.61,1:23:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来点什么呢 先生?\N{\rEng}What'll it be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.14,1:23:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那只咬过我的狗 它身上的毛 (注: 以毒攻毒之意)\N{\rEng}Hair of the dog that bit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.81,1:23:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,加冰的波本酒\N{\rEng}Bourbon on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.32,1:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么办\N{\rEng}That'll do her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.24,1:23:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不收您的钱 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}No charge to you, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.94,1:23:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不收钱?\N{\rEng}No charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.54,1:23:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,您的钱在这里用不上\N{\rEng}Your money's no good here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.18,1:23:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是房子的命令\N{\rEng}Orders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.12,1:24:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,房子的命令\N{\rEng}Orders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.86,1:24:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喝光吧 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Drink up, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.07,1:24:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那种喜欢知道 是谁在帮谁买酒的人 罗伊德\N{\rEng}I'm the kind of man likes to know who's buying their drinks, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.91,1:24:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那与你无关 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}It's not a matter that concerns you, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.05,1:24:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,至少 在这点上无关\N{\rEng}At least, not at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.79,1:24:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么说 罗伊德\N{\rEng}Anything you say, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.62,1:24:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么说\N{\rEng}Anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.61,1:24:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天啊! 我真的很抱歉 先生\N{\rEng}Oh, dear! I'm so sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.18,1:24:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我的天!\N{\rEng}Oh, dear. Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.85,1:24:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我把您的夹克弄得一团糟 先生\N{\rEng}I've made an awful mess of your jacket, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.65,1:24:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我有很多的夹克\N{\rEng}That's all right. I've got plenty of jackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.49,1:25:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是蛋酒 先生 它常常会留下污点\N{\rEng}I'm afraid it's advocaat, sir. It tends to stain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.49,1:25:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋酒 是吗?\N{\rEng}Advocaat, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.83,1:25:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生 我想最好的办法...\N{\rEng}Yes, sir. I think the best thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.20,1:25:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是去男洗手间...\N{\rEng}...is to come along to the gentlemen's room...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.60,1:25:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们用水擦一下 先生\N{\rEng}...and we'll get some water to it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.97,1:25:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好像你身上也沾了一点...\N{\rEng}Looks like you might have got a spot of it on yourself...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.48,1:25:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛西老伙计\N{\rEng}...Jeevesy old boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.68,1:25:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那没关系 先生 您比较重要\N{\rEng}That doesn't matter, sir. You're the important one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.15,1:25:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说真是太好了\N{\rEng}Awfully nice of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.98,1:25:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我想过在晚会前\N{\rEng}Of course, I intended to change my jacket this evening...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.06,1:25:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,换件夹克...\N{\rEng}...before the fish and goose soiree.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.52,1:25:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很明智 先生 非常明智\N{\rEng}Very wise, sir. Very wise.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.76,1:25:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿 我帮你...\N{\rEng}Here. I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.90,1:25:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着这个 杰佛西\N{\rEng}...hold this for you there, Jeevesy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.37,1:25:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you, sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.20,1:25:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看看沾点水是不是会好些 先生\N{\rEng}Let's see if we can improve this with a little water, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.04,1:25:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我把...\N{\rEng}All right. I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.51,1:25:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的波本酒和蛋酒放在这儿\N{\rEng}...set my bourbon and advocaat down right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.28,1:25:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,耽误不了您不多久时间\N{\rEng}Won't keep you a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.92,1:25:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.39,1:25:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么叫你的呢 杰佛西?\N{\rEng}What do they call you, Jeevesy?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.26,1:25:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第 先生 戴伯特·格瑞第\N{\rEng}Grady, sir. Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.60,1:26:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第?\N{\rEng}Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.63,1:26:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.14,1:26:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,戴伯特·格瑞第\N{\rEng}Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.67,1:26:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对 先生\N{\rEng}That's right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.92,1:26:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第先生...\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.12,1:26:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我该不会以前在哪儿见过你吧?\N{\rEng}...haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.42,1:26:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...? 不是 先生 我不这么认为\N{\rEng}Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.17,1:26:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,擦掉了 先生\N{\rEng}It's coming off now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.94,1:26:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第先生...\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.01,1:26:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是曾经担任过这里的看管员吗?\N{\rEng}...weren't you once the caretaker here?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.68,1:26:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...? 不是 先生 我不这么认为\N{\rEng}Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.52,1:26:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚了 是吗 格瑞第先生?\N{\rEng}You a married man, are you, Mr. Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.06,1:26:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.09,1:26:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我有妻子和两个女儿 先生\N{\rEng}I have a wife and two daughters, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.40,1:26:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那...\N{\rEng}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.60,1:27:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她们现在在哪里?\N{\rEng}...where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.07,1:27:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她们就在附近的某个地方 我现在也不能确定\N{\rEng}They're somewhere around. I'm not quite sure at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.32,1:27:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第先生...\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.82,1:27:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾是这里的看管员\N{\rEng}You were the caretaker here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.69,1:27:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我认出你了\N{\rEng}I recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.06,1:27:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在报纸上看到过你的照片\N{\rEng}I saw your picture in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.57,1:27:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你...\N{\rEng}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.80,1:27:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的妻子和女儿剁成碎片\N{\rEng}...chopped your wife and daughter up into little bits.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.84,1:27:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...\N{\rEng}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.88,1:27:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你把你自己的脑袋轰掉了\N{\rEng}...then you blew your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.72,1:27:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那真奇怪 先生\N{\rEng}That's strange, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.49,1:27:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这个完全没有一点印象\N{\rEng}I don't have any recollection of that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.90,1:27:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第先生...\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.20,1:28:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾是这里的看管员\N{\rEng}...you were the caretaker here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.35,1:28:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我和你不一样 先生\N{\rEng}I'm sorry to differ with you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.99,1:28:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你...\N{\rEng}But you...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.46,1:28:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,才是看管员\N{\rEng}...are the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.56,1:28:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都是看管员\N{\rEng}You've always been the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.37,1:28:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该知道 先生\N{\rEng}I should know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.64,1:28:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在这里\N{\rEng}I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.46,1:28:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 特朗斯先生...\N{\rEng}Did you know, Mr. Torrance...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.90,1:28:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的儿子...\N{\rEng}...that your son...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.07,1:28:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,正试图带外面的一帮人...\N{\rEng}...is attempting to bring an outside party...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.97,1:29:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,加入到这里来?\N{\rEng}...into this situation?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.75,1:29:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个吗?\N{\rEng}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.69,1:29:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他正是 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}He is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.13,1:29:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谁?\N{\rEng}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.53,1:29:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑鬼\N{\rEng}A nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.24,1:29:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑鬼?\N{\rEng}A nigger?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.38,1:29:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑鬼...\N{\rEng}A nigger...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.01,1:29:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,厨子\N{\rEng}...cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.62,1:29:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么带法?\N{\rEng}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.16,1:29:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的儿子...\N{\rEng}Your son...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.36,1:29:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有一种非常好的天赋\N{\rEng}...has a very great talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.13,1:29:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你都不知道那有多高\N{\rEng}I don't think you are aware how great it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.37,1:29:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但他正在试图使用他的天赋...\N{\rEng}But he is attempting to use that very talent...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.81,1:29:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,用来反抗你的意旨\N{\rEng}...against your will.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.32,1:30:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好...\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.36,1:30:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个很任性的孩子\N{\rEng}...he is a very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.83,1:30:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他的确是 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Indeed he is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.43,1:30:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一个非常任性的孩子\N{\rEng}A very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.54,1:30:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一个很...\N{\rEng}A rather...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.07,1:30:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,顽皮的孩子...\N{\rEng}...naughty boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.81,1:30:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果允许我大胆的说 先生\N{\rEng}...if I may be so bold, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.25,1:30:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是她妈妈\N{\rEng}It's his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.16,1:30:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她...\N{\rEng}She...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.83,1:30:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,妨碍我\N{\rEng}...interferes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.93,1:30:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也许需要跟他们好好的...\N{\rEng}Perhaps they need a good...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.24,1:30:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谈一谈\N{\rEng}...talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.27,1:30:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果...\N{\rEng}If...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.31,1:30:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不介意我这么说的话\N{\rEng}...you don't mind my saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.88,1:30:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也许...\N{\rEng}Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.05,1:31:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,光谈还不够\N{\rEng}...a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.95,1:31:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的姑娘们 先生...\N{\rEng}My girls, sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.39,1:31:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她们开始不喜欢遥望旅馆\N{\rEng}...they didn't care for the Overlook at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.86,1:31:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个最后偷了包火柴...\N{\rEng}One of them actually stole a pack of matches...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.96,1:31:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想把旅馆烧了\N{\rEng}...and tried to burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.70,1:31:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我...\N{\rEng}But I...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.57,1:31:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,纠正了她们 先生\N{\rEng}...corrected them, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.87,1:31:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当我的妻子阻止我 达成我的使命的时候...\N{\rEng}And when my wife tried to prevent me from doing my duty...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.21,1:31:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\rEng}...I...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.48,1:31:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,纠正了她\N{\rEng}...corrected her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.83,1:31:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有雪地车\N{\rEng}We have the Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.17,1:31:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果天气稍微变好...\N{\rEng}If the weather breaks...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.14,1:31:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就能...\N{\rEng}...we might just be able...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.11,1:31:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,下山去了\N{\rEng}...to get down the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.85,1:32:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以先给林务员打电话...\N{\rEng}I could call the forest rangers first...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.02,1:32:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我们来了\N{\rEng}...and...tell them that we're coming...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.89,1:32:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样...\N{\rEng}....so that...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.26,1:32:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们后来没到达 他们就会来找我们\N{\rEng}...they could start searching for us in case we didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.14,1:32:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果杰克不陪我们走的话...\N{\rEng}And if Jack won't come with us...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.77,1:32:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有告诉他 我们自己走了\N{\rEng}...I'll just have to tell him that we're going by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.71,1:32:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么办了\N{\rEng}That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.05,1:32:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Redrum红酒 (注:谋杀-Murder的倒写)\N{\rEng}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.52,1:32:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Redrum红酒\N{\rEng}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.43,1:32:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 宝贝?\N{\rEng}What's the matter, hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.80,1:32:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Redrum红酒!\N{\rEng}Redrum!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.90,1:32:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做恶梦吗?\N{\rEng}Are you having a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.91,1:32:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝?\N{\rEng}Hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.95,1:33:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼不在这儿 特朗斯太太\N{\rEng}Danny's not here, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.86,1:33:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 宝贝\N{\rEng}Come on, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.37,1:33:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒啊\N{\rEng}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.74,1:33:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是做了个恶梦\N{\rEng}You just had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.41,1:33:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.61,1:33:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼不能醒来了 特朗斯太太\N{\rEng}Danny can't wake up, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.96,1:33:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒!\N{\rEng}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.93,1:33:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.47,1:33:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在\N{\rEng}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.47,1:33:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒!\N{\rEng}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.88,1:33:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼离开了 特朗斯太太\N{\rEng}Danny's gone away, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.03,1:34:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12\N{\rEng}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.10,1:34:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.34,1:34:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你有收到吗?\N{\rEng}Are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.31,1:34:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12\N{\rEng}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.11,1:34:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.12,1:34:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听到我说话吗?\N{\rEng}Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.16,1:34:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12\N{\rEng}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.39,1:34:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.16,1:34:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有收到吗?\N{\rEng}Are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.37,1:35:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 森林服务台\N{\rEng}Good evening. Forest service.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.44,1:35:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是迪克·霍洛朗\N{\rEng}This is Dick Hallorann again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.88,1:35:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才打了电话联系遥望旅馆的人\N{\rEng}I called a while ago about the folks at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.22,1:35:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试图联系他们多次 但都没有回应\N{\rEng}We tried to contact them several times but they didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.22,1:35:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可能他们没有开无线电 也可能是没听到\N{\rEng}Maybe they got their radio turned off or they can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.03,1:35:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得有必要 我待会儿再呼叫他们\N{\rEng}If you'd like, I'd be glad to try again later on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.43,1:35:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你人真好\N{\rEng}That's very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.77,1:35:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会儿再打给你\N{\rEng}I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.74,1:35:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.86,1:36:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 小姐 我们什么时候才能到丹佛?\N{\rEng}Pardon me, miss. What time will we get to Denver?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.10,1:36:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,预计是8点20分到达 先生\N{\rEng}We're due to arrive at 8:20, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.47,1:36:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\rEng}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.98,1:37:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,杜瑞凯的修车场\N{\rEng}Durkin's Garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.11,1:37:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我找赖利\N{\rEng}Can I speak to Larry?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.45,1:37:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请说\N{\rEng}Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.71,1:37:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 赖利 我是迪克 迪克·霍洛朗\N{\rEng}Hi, Larry. This is Dick. Dick Hallorann.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.48,1:37:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克! 你好吗?\N{\rEng}Dick! How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.35,1:37:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那边天气怎么样?\N{\rEng}How's the weather down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.92,1:37:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我没在佛罗里达 我在斯塔普列顿机场给你打电话\N{\rEng}I'm not in Florida. I'm calling from Stapleton Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.46,1:37:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那儿干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.49,1:37:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚从迈阿密来 我今天要去遥望旅馆\N{\rEng}I just got in from Miami. I got to get to the Overlook today.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.13,1:37:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那里天气如何?\N{\rEng}What's the weather like there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.40,1:38:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,扫雪机不断在运作 货物还是能运进城...\N{\rEng}The snowplows are keeping things moving in town...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.47,1:38:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是山路全被封死了\N{\rEng}...but the mountain roads are blocked.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.94,1:38:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我找辆雪地车上去\N{\rEng}Then I'm going to need a Snowcat to get up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.84,1:38:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你能给我弄出一辆吗?\N{\rEng}Can you fix me up with one?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.88,1:38:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,出了什么大事 非得今天上那儿...?\N{\rEng}What's the big deal about getting there today...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.18,1:38:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是在这种天气?\N{\rEng}...especially in this weather?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.62,1:38:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,赖利 只在你我之间说说 我们遇上了很严重的问题...\N{\rEng}Larry, just between you and me, we got a very serious problem...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.29,1:38:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,关于看管那个地方的人\N{\rEng}...with the people taking care of the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.73,1:38:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根本就在打混摸鱼\N{\rEng}They turned out to be completely unreliable assholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.80,1:38:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,尤尔曼先生昨晚给我打了电话\N{\rEng}Ullman phoned me last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.80,1:38:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,委派我去看看 是不是该把他们换掉! ?\N{\rEng}And I'm supposed to find out if they have to be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.64,1:38:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要多久你才能到那里?\N{\rEng}How long will it take you to get here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.01,1:38:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大概五小时\N{\rEng}About five hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.88,1:38:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在机场租辆车\N{\rEng}I'm going to rent a car here at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.61,1:38:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好 雪地车我会想办法\N{\rEng}Okay, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.55,1:38:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 赖利 我真的非常感激\N{\rEng}Thanks, Larry. I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.59,1:38:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧 开车小心些\N{\rEng}That's all right. Drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.89,1:38:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,您正在收听的是丹佛63号电台 哈尔和查理为您播报\N{\rEng}You're with Hal and Charlie on Radio 63, KHOW, Denver.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.36,1:38:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,天气很糟\N{\rEng}And we have a bad day out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.14,1:38:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,丹佛市中区普降大雪\N{\rEng}Heavy snow throughout the Denver metro area.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.71,1:39:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很多的入山关口...\N{\rEng}Many mountain passes...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.41,1:39:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,狼溪和红山的关口被关闭...\N{\rEng}... Wolf Creek and Red Mountain passes are closed...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.48,1:39:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,连带也影响了艾森豪威尔隧道\N{\rEng}...and the chain law is in effect at the Eisenhower Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.98,1:39:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从新闻部门获悉...\N{\rEng}We hear from the news department...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.85,1:39:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只有少数几架飞机 降落在斯塔普列顿机场...\N{\rEng}...only a few flights are landing at Stapleton Airport...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.26,1:39:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在这样的暴风雪天气...\N{\rEng}...and with storms like this...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.06,1:39:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想机场会在一个小时内 完全关闭\N{\rEng}...I guess the entire airport will be closed within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.36,1:39:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雪会持续一整天 气象局...\N{\rEng}The storm will continue through the day and the Weather Service...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.43,1:39:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,已发布了 针对所有丹佛城周边地区的...\N{\rEng}...has declared a stockman's and traveler's advisory...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.10,1:39:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,旅客和牧人的通告\N{\rEng}...for all areas outlying the Denver metro region.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.11,1:39:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把乳牛关在棚里\N{\rEng}Get the cows in the barn.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.97,1:39:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝?\N{\rEng}Hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.01,1:39:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 就一分钟 好吗?\N{\rEng}Listen to me for a minute, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.25,1:40:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去和爸爸谈几分钟...\N{\rEng}I'm just going to go and talk to Daddy for a few minutes...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.15,1:40:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很快回来\N{\rEng}...and I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.16,1:40:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你就待在这儿...\N{\rEng}I want you to just stay here...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.89,1:40:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的动画片 好吗?\N{\rEng}...and watch your cartoons, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.50,1:40:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗 宝贝?\N{\rEng}Okay, hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.27,1:40:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好 特朗斯太太\N{\rEng}Yes, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.92,1:40:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.19,1:40:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概只要五分钟就回来\N{\rEng}I'll be back in just about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.89,1:40:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我出去的时候会把门给锁上\N{\rEng}I'm going to lock the door behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.15,1:42:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只有工作 没有玩乐 杰克呆若木鸡!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.63,1:43:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只有工作 没有玩乐 杰克呆若木鸡!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.60,1:44:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你说好不好呢?\N{\rEng}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.91,1:44:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好不好呢?\N{\rEng}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.39,1:44:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这下面做什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.43,1:44:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\rEng}I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.24,1:44:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想...\N{\rEng}...wanted...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.71,1:44:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和你谈谈\N{\rEng}...to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.81,1:44:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.68,1:44:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就谈吧\N{\rEng}Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.96,1:45:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你想谈什么呢?\N{\rEng}What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.87,1:45:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是记不得了\N{\rEng}I can't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.84,1:45:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你记不得了\N{\rEng}You can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.78,1:45:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不行...\N{\rEng}No...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.48,1:45:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\rEng}...I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.19,1:45:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是关于丹尼?\N{\rEng}Maybe it was about Danny?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.83,1:45:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是关于他\N{\rEng}Maybe it was about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.17,1:45:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们该讨论一下丹尼\N{\rEng}I think we should discuss Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.28,1:45:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想...\N{\rEng}I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.48,1:45:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该讨论一下 应该拿他怎么办才好\N{\rEng}...we should discuss what should be done with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.95,1:45:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,应该拿他怎么办?\N{\rEng}What should be done with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.53,1:46:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.83,1:46:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为那不是真的\N{\rEng}I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.04,1:46:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你有一些很明确的想法...\N{\rEng}I think you have some very definite ideas...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.84,1:46:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,关于应该拿丹尼怎么办\N{\rEng}...about what should be done with Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.74,1:46:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道究竟是些什么\N{\rEng}And I'd like to know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.25,1:46:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我...\N{\rEng}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.35,1:46:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也许该带他去看医生\N{\rEng}...I think maybe he should be taken to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.95,1:46:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为"也许"该带他去看医生?\N{\rEng}You think "maybe" he should be taken to a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.49,1:46:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么时候开始想 "也许"该带他去看医生的?\N{\rEng}When do you think "maybe" he should be taken to a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.47,1:46:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快?\N{\rEng}As soon as possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.43,1:46:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"尽快? "\N{\rEng}"As soon as possible?"
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.44,1:46:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.28,1:46:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信他的健康有严重问题?\N{\rEng}You believe his health might be at stake.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.12,1:46:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.99,1:46:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你很关心他\N{\rEng}And you are concerned about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.19,1:46:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那你关心我吗?\N{\rEng}And are you concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.26,1:46:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然关心\N{\rEng}Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.63,1:46:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然关心!\N{\rEng}Of course you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.07,1:47:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你可曾想过我的责任吗?\N{\rEng}Have you ever thought about my responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.40,1:47:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么?\N{\rEng}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.11,1:47:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有想过 就一分钟...\N{\rEng}Have you ever had a single moment's...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.14,1:47:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想过我的责任?\N{\rEng}...thought about my responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.41,1:47:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有片刻想过...\N{\rEng}Have you ever thought for a single moment...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.88,1:47:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我对我的雇主的责任? !\N{\rEng}...about my responsibilities to my employers?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.95,1:47:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经同意...\N{\rEng}Has is ever occurred to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.99,1:47:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看管这座旅馆直到5月1号?\N{\rEng}...that I have agreed to look after the hotel until May 1st?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.73,1:47:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,它跟你有关系吗...\N{\rEng}Does it matter to you at all...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.96,1:47:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是主人完全信任我...\N{\rEng}...that the owners have placed their complete confidence in me...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.27,1:47:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我签了契约...\N{\rEng}...and that I have signed a letter of agreement...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.60,1:47:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里面我接受了委任?\N{\rEng}...in which I've accepted that responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.67,1:47:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否有哪怕是最卑微的一点理解...\N{\rEng}Do you have the slightest idea...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.91,1:47:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,关于什么是伦理道德的精髓? 你有吗?\N{\rEng}...what a moral and ethical principal is? Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.51,1:47:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你可曾想过 会对我的前途产生什么影响...\N{\rEng}Has it ever occurred to you what would happen to my future...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.82,1:47:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不能带着我的责任快乐的生活?\N{\rEng}...if I fail to live up to my responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.42,1:47:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可曾想过那样的事? 可曾想过? !\N{\rEng}Has it ever occurred to you? Has it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.92,1:47:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.33,1:47:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.69,1:47:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回我的房间了\N{\rEng}I just want to go back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.86,1:47:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.77,1:47:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.77,1:48:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我很困惑\N{\rEng}...I'm very confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.94,1:48:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要找个机会把事情想清楚\N{\rEng}And I just need a chance to think things over.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.64,1:48:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以用他妈的一辈子时间 去把事情想清楚!\N{\rEng}You've had your whole fucking life to think things over!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.78,1:48:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这几分钟又怎么够用?\N{\rEng}What good's a few minutes more going to do you now?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.52,1:48:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.36,1:48:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你!\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.43,1:48:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别伤害我\N{\rEng}Don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.69,1:48:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你\N{\rEng}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.23,1:48:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.63,1:48:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.70,1:48:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\rEng}Darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.90,1:48:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我生命的亮光\N{\rEng}Light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.90,1:48:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你\N{\rEng}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.44,1:48:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不让我说完\N{\rEng}You didn't let me finish my sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.64,1:48:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我说: "我不会伤害你"\N{\rEng}I said, "I'm not going to hurt you."
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.04,1:48:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想锤你的头\N{\rEng}I'm just going to bash your brains in.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.08,1:48:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想一边办事一边重锤\N{\rEng}I'm going to bash them right the fuck in.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.12,1:48:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.19,1:48:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.42,1:48:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你\N{\rEng}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.09,1:48:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.86,1:48:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!\N{\rEng}Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.79,1:48:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你!\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.06,1:48:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别挥那根球棒!\N{\rEng}Stop swinging the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.03,1:48:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\rEng}Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.07,1:48:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把那根球棒放下 温蒂\N{\rEng}Put that bat down, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.57,1:48:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来!\N{\rEng}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.54,1:49:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把球棒给我\N{\rEng}Give me the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.88,1:49:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你!\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.24,1:49:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走开! - 把球棒给我\N{\rEng}- Stay away! - Give me the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.65,1:49:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,停!\N{\rEng}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.95,1:49:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把球棒给我\N{\rEng}Give me the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.72,1:49:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走开 - 球棒别乱挥\N{\rEng}- Stay away from me. - Stop swinging the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.55,1:49:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你停下来\N{\rEng}Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.12,1:49:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,把球棒给我\N{\rEng}Give me the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.52,1:49:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\rEng}Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.03,1:49:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 停下来! - 把球棒给我\N{\rEng}- Stop it! - Give me the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.80,1:49:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼!\N{\rEng}Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.12,1:50:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.62,1:50:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rEng}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.49,1:50:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.33,1:50:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.45,1:51:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rEng}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.32,1:51:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.16,1:51:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\rEng}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.19,1:51:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼!\N{\rEng}Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.43,1:51:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去! 开门!\N{\rEng}Let me out of here! Open the goddamn door!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.70,1:51:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂 听着\N{\rEng}Wendy, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.37,1:51:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去 我会把整件事忘掉\N{\rEng}Let me out and I'll forget the whole goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.51,1:51:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就当什么也没有发生过\N{\rEng}It'll be just like nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.66,1:51:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\rEng}Baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.23,1:51:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你真的对我的头下了重手\N{\rEng}I think you hurt my head real bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.14,1:51:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我头昏\N{\rEng}I'm dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.81,1:51:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要个医生\N{\rEng}I need a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.88,1:52:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,甜心\N{\rEng}Honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.76,1:52:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我留在这儿\N{\rEng}Don't leave me in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.70,1:52:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要走了\N{\rEng}I'm going to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.67,1:52:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天要...\N{\rEng}I'm going to try...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.71,1:52:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,用雪地车带丹尼下山...\N{\rEng}...to get Danny down the Sidewinder...in the Snowcat today.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.02,1:52:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带个医生回来\N{\rEng}I'll bring back a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.65,1:52:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂\N{\rEng}Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.23,1:52:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要走了\N{\rEng}I'm going to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.10,1:52:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 温蒂 - 干嘛?\N{\rEng}- Wendy. - yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.54,1:52:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你会有个大惊喜\N{\rEng}You've got a big surprise coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.81,1:52:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪儿都去不了\N{\rEng}You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.08,1:53:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看雪地车吧 还有无线电 你会明白我的意思的\N{\rEng}Go check out the Snowcat and the radio, and you'll see what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.83,1:53:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看\N{\rEng}Go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.66,1:53:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看!\N{\rEng}Go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.24,1:53:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看\N{\rEng}Go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.03,1:55:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是格瑞第 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}It's Grady, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.17,1:55:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔伯特·格瑞第\N{\rEng}Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.71,1:55:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,格瑞第?\N{\rEng}Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.67,1:55:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 格瑞第\N{\rEng}Hello, Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.17,1:55:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,特朗斯先生...\N{\rEng}Mr. Torrance...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.91,1:55:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你很难办好...\N{\rEng}...I see you can hardly have taken care of the...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.38,1:55:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先前讨论的事\N{\rEng}...business we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.59,1:56:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要说第二遍 格瑞第先生\N{\rEng}No need to rub it in, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.40,1:56:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我一出去 就会处理现在的情况\N{\rEng}I'll deal with that situation as soon as I get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.34,1:56:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你确实会 特朗斯先生?\N{\rEng}Will you indeed, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.57,1:56:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道\N{\rEng}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.58,1:56:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我有几个疑点\N{\rEng}I have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.88,1:56:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我 还有其他人 都相信...\N{\rEng}I, and others, have come to believe...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.32,1:56:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心没在这里\N{\rEng}...that your heart is not in this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.96,1:56:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你对它没胃口\N{\rEng}That you haven't the belly for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.67,1:56:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我个机会证明它 格瑞第先生\N{\rEng}Just give me one more chance to prove it, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.81,1:56:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我全部的要求\N{\rEng}That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.28,1:56:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妻子看来比我们想像要来得强 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}Your wife appears to be stronger than we imagined, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.75,1:56:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要更...\N{\rEng}Somewhat more...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.42,1:56:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,机灵一点\N{\rEng}...resourceful.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.66,1:56:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好像她胜过你\N{\rEng}She seems to have got the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.66,1:56:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一会儿 格瑞第先生\N{\rEng}For the moment, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.07,1:57:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就只这一会儿\N{\rEng}Only for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.14,1:57:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕你得用一种最粗野的方式...\N{\rEng}I fear you will have to deal with this matter...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.58,1:57:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,来处理这件事 特朗斯先生\N{\rEng}...in the harshest possible way, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.81,1:57:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕...\N{\rEng}I fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.65,1:57:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一可做的事了\N{\rEng}...that is the only thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.69,1:57:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,再没有比这...\N{\rEng}There's nothing I look forward to...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.99,1:57:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,更让人愉快的事 格瑞第先生\N{\rEng}...with greater pleasure, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.30,1:57:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你保证 不是吗 特朗斯先生?\N{\rEng}You give your word on that, do you, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.50,1:57:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\rEng}I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.66,1:58:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Redrum红酒 (注:Murder谋杀的倒写)\N{\rEng}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.16,1:58:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Redrum红酒\N{\rEng}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.71,2:01:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼 别这样!\N{\rEng}Danny, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.08,2:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家了\N{\rEng}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.89,2:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 出来 不管你在哪儿\N{\rEng}Come out, come out, wherever you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:05.33,2:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我出不去\N{\rEng}I can't get out.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.00,2:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑!\N{\rEng}Run!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.96,2:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 躲起来!\N{\rEng}Run and hide!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.94,2:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑!\N{\rEng}Run!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.27,2:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快!\N{\rEng}Quick!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.21,2:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小猪 小猪 让我进去\N{\rEng}Little pigs, little pigs, let me come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.48,2:03:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你下巴上的毛?\N{\rEng}Not by the hair on your chinny-chin-chin?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.42,2:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我要生气了...\N{\rEng}Then I'll huff...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.69,2:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,接着我要喘气了...\N{\rEng}...and I'll puff...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.80,2:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我要毁了你的房子 冲进去!\N{\rEng}...and I'll blow your house in!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.78,2:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你!\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.89,2:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要!\N{\rEng}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.32,2:03:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要!\N{\rEng}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.44,2:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来!\N{\rEng}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.92,2:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼来了!\N{\rEng}Here's Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.44,2:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.12,2:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在吗?\N{\rEng}Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.98,2:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.86,2:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在吗?\N{\rEng}Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.66,2:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在吗?\N{\rEng}Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.61,2:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼男孩!\N{\rEng}Danny-boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.17,2:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了!\N{\rEng}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.61,2:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 小丹!\N{\rEng}I'm coming, Dan!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.35,2:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死人的宴会 不是吗?\N{\rEng}Great party, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.40,2:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了!\N{\rEng}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:20.21,2:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的!\N{\rEng}You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.38,2:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在你后面!\N{\rEng}I'm right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.26,2:17:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈咪! - 丹尼 到这儿来!\N{\rEng}- Mommy! - Danny, come here!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.50,2:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\rEng}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:40.58,2:17:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪...?\N{\rEng}Where...?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.86,2:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂!\N{\rEng}Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.35,2:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等!\N{\rEng}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:51.87,2:18:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要!\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:53.87,2:18:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,救命!\N{\rEng}Help!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.36,2:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂!\N{\rEng}Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.35,2:19:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我!\N{\rEng}Help!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.85,2:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,求你...\N{\rEng}Please...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.84,2:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂\N{\rEng}Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.41,2:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\rEng}Help.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:22.90,2:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.16,2:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,遥望旅馆1921年7月4日舞会

